            <h1 class="display-3">Statistics</h1>
            <h2 class="v-header">Why Websites?</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="v-section vedauritron">
    <div class="row v-section-content">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <h2 class="v-header">Technology Evolves</h2>
            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                <p class="mb-0">
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">
                        <li>
                            91% of customers have visited a store because of an online experience.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            80% of internet users own a smartphone. Responsive websites are a <i>must</i>.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Online Marketing is cheaper than other types of paid-marketing.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            68% of consumers who conduct local searches go to a store within
                            24 hours and 49% make a purchase within the next 24 hours.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
            </blockquote>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="v-section">
    <div class="row v-section-content">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <h1 class="display-3">Projects</h1>
            <h2 class="v-header">Currently In Development</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="v-section vedauritron">
    <div class="row v-section-content">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <h2 class="v-header">Everlasting Aesthetics</h2>
            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                <p class="mb-0">
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin-left: 0px;">
                        <li>
                            Guest, Member, Nurse and Administrator Accounts
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Automated Appointment Scheduling
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Event Management and RSVP
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Personal Work Schedule
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Update Content in Real-Time
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Data Driven Tables
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Searchable Data
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Scalable Website Application
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
            </blockquote>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="v-section vedauritron">
    <div class="row v-section-content">
        <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <h2 class="v-header">Our Take</h2>
            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                <p class="mb-0">
                    This amazing website application helps nurses automatically book appointments, manage their
                    services, events, accounts and more.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    Our client wanted a friendly, easy to navigate website application that can replace
                    multiple applications they already use.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    We are automating scheduling and newsletters. We're coding solutions to allow managing their listed
                    services and events straight from their website administrator accounts. This is seriously a powerful
                    website application that we're proud of.
                </p>
            </blockquote>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="v-section">
    <div class="row v-section-content">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div class="jumbotron-fluid smalltron">
                <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="3"></li>
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="4"></li>
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="5"></li>
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="6"></li>
                    </ol>
                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                        <div class="carousel-item active">
                            <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/img/portfolio/web/ea_01.JPG" alt="FirstSlide" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/img/portfolio/web/ea_02.JPG" alt="FirstSlide" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/img/portfolio/web/ea_03.JPG" alt="FirstSlide" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/img/portfolio/web/ea_05.JPG" alt="FirstSlide" />
